25
00:05:34,674 --> 00:05:36,092
Adakah anda hilang akal?

26
00:05:36,540 --> 00:05:38,250
Anda sangat degil!

27
00:05:39,178 --> 00:05:40,972
Saya sudah memberi amaran kepada anda tentang dia!

28
